Parteiensysteme Bundesl√§nder

library(knitr)

Quellen

  • Schniewind, Aline. 2008. ‚ÄòParteiensysteme‚Äô. SS. 63-109 in Die Demokratien der deutschen Bundesl√§nder: Politische Institutionen im Vergleich, Hrsg. Markus Freitag und Adrian Vatter. UTB, Stuttgart.
  • Schr√∂der, Valentin. 2018. ‚ÄúWahlen in Deutschland.‚Äù wahlen-in-deutschland.de.

Parameter

Effektive Parteienzahl (EPZ)

\(EPZ = \frac{1}{\sum_{i=1}^{n} p_i^2}\)

  • \(p_i\) ‚Äì Anteil der Parlamentsmandate der einzelnen Parteien
  • \(n\) ‚Äì Anzahl der im Parlament vertretenen Parteien

Volatilit√§t (Pedersen-Index)

\(V = \sum_{i=1}^{n} \frac{ | ( V_{it} - V_{i(t-1)} ) | }{ 2 }\)

  • \(V_{it}\) ‚Äì W√§hlerstimmenanteil Partei \(i\) zum Zeitpunkt \(t\)
  • \(V_{i(t-1)}\) ‚Äì W√§hlerstimmenanteil Partei \(i\) zum Zeitpunkt \(t-1\)
  • Wertebereich Indikator \(V\) ‚Äì 0% bis 100%

Polarisierung

  • Beispiel ‚Äì Konzentration von W√§hlerstimmen auf gro√üe Parteien (CDU und SPD)
  • weitere Parameter Polarisierung siehe Schniewind (2008, 80‚Äî82)
wid_raw <- read_csv("daten/wahlen-in-dtl/wid-ergebnisse.csv")
laender <- read_csv("daten/wahlen-in-dtl/state_names.csv")

date_prev <- 
  wid_raw %>% 
  distinct(state, date) %>% 
  mutate(
    date = as.character(date),
    date_prev = lag(date),
    date_prev = ifelse(date > date_prev, date_prev, NA),
    date_prev = as.Date(date_prev)
    )

vote_prev <- 
  wid_raw %>% 
  select(date_prev = date, state, party, vote_share_prev = votes_p)

wid <- 
  wid_raw %>% 
  mutate(
        date = as.character(date),
        seats_share = round(100 * seats / seatstotal, 2)
    ) %>% 
  select(widvote_id:date, party, vote_share = votes_p, seats_share) %>% 
  left_join(date_prev) %>% 
  left_join(vote_prev) %>% 
  left_join(laender)

write_csv(wid, "wid-laender-ergebnisse.csv")
cdu_spd <- 
  wid %>%
  filter(party %in% c("cdu", "csu", "spd")) %>% 
  group_by(state_name, date) %>% 
  summarise(cdu_spd = sum(vote_share, na.rm = TRUE))

wid_param <- 
  wid %>%
  group_by(state_name, date) %>% 
  summarise(
    epz = 1 / sum((vote_share/100)^2, na.rm = TRUE),
    volatilitaet = sum(abs(vote_share - vote_share_prev) / 2, na.rm = TRUE)
  ) %>% 
  left_join(cdu_spd) %>% 
  mutate_if(is.numeric, round, 1)

write_csv(wid_param, "wid-laender-parameter.csv")

wid_param_dec <- 
  wid_param %>% 
  mutate(decade = round(lubridate::year(date) / 10) * 10) %>% 
  group_by(state_name, decade) %>% 
  summarise_if(is.numeric, ~ round(mean(., na.rm = TRUE), 1))

Parameter f√ºr ausgew√§hlte L√§nder seit 1950

pl_states <- c("Baden-W√ºrttemberg", "Berlin", "Bremen", "Nordrhein-Westfalen")
pl_df <- wid_param %>%
  filter(state_name %in% pl_states) %>%
  mutate(year = lubridate::year(date))

plot_param <- function(parameter) {
  ggplot(pl_df, aes_string(x = "year", y = parameter, color = "state_name")) + 
    geom_line() + 
    geom_point(color = "darkgrey", size = 1)
}
plot_param("epz")

plot_param("volatilitaet")

plot_param("cdu_spd")
